            <title><![CDATA[张艾嘉凭《灯火阑珊》夺金马奖最佳女主角]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-11/121557.jpg?itok=fmmjBTE_" title="张艾嘉今晚凭《灯火阑珊》夺金马奖最佳女主角。图为《灯火阑珊》剧照。（互联网）" alt="张艾嘉今晚凭《灯火阑珊》夺金马奖最佳女主角。图为《灯火阑珊》剧照。（互联网）" src="https://www.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-11/121557.jpg?itok=fmmjBTE_" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
